Comments: Summer may seem far away, but planning a road trip with kids requires months of planning. We've done the research for you and picked out a few of the more hidden gems across the United States for you to visit with your family. From sand sledding to cave mining, museums to farms, we've compiled 49 attractions all over the country that offer your kiddos unique experiences involving education, play, and simple, pure enjoyment.

The Delaware Outdoor Trail is an easy-to-follow passport-style system that leads visitors methodically through an array of outdoor activities! Enjoy more than 60 activities in over 40 statewide locations.
